{"tid":1787190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲講新年快樂?2020香港第一秒","createTime":"2019-12-17T17:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T18:17:13.000Z","uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c682a24a651e4c04e0d8151b14469c084919342a","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:46:10.000Z","msg":"第一秒 五<br />\n第二秒 大<br />\n第三秒 訴<br />\n第四秒 求<br />\n第五秒 缺<br />\n第六秒 一<br />\n第七秒 不<br />\n第八秒 可<br />\n<br />\n當然記得之前仲有<br />\n10,9,光,復,香,港,時,代,革,命!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比埋天文台網上時鐘你喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/tc/gts/time/clock_e.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fgts%2Ftime%2Fclock_e.html&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BustNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=2d4db615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/tc/gts/time/clock_e.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好開心又一年喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但慶祝之餘，<br />\n所有付出過嘅手足 、<br />\n所有流落黎嘅汗水、<br />\n所有不能眠的晚上。<br />\n仲有其他好多野都<br />\n不能忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不應忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不可忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻手足被捕人數已超過在囚人士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而濫捕情況一直持續。<br />\n我好希望香港人記住 <br />\n仲<br />\n未<br />\n完<br />\n架 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2348855f6efc44c8495c56a97e51e6bb59fb4162","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:47:28.000Z","msg":"係呀 新一年好開心<br />\n記得唔係新一年就咩事都係過咗去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a6d8b738c765db333d3892c0bd0a666e05387f","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"fd9e2bc01896fb77c62df792e9269cc2aea76479","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:49:18.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"269cfaf44f72458ed7b88c6135b204fcf2e16f7e","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:49:29.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"5e46777e960f59dcd1b4ba9bdfe07aaed89d5253","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:49:40.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"74b83e54faf8ff006ee460a46ba063b17f4ef66a","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:49:50.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"23b5978c31a8d00691940774c5ccdc41aaa1a8ff","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:50:01.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"a88103259c71a72eb4e9d88221c4f919240b5dd7","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"2b43be17284f175e225f4493ec869bbd64467949","tid":1787190,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:50:22.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"ab2879d93a2ea9a97fff70e90be2ba8b80099d00","tid":1787190,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T18:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}